{"tid":2064851,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"【抗爭一週年】《Petals Rain 漫天紛花》Lyric Video + 中文字幕 [Demo Version]","createTime":"2020-06-15T06:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T10:45:52.000Z","uid":322240,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b1cdad7959cf57e87c78953f15c34c4088d99e4e","tid":2064851,"uid":322240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T06:06:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4D1Oeh0smuQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4D1Oeh0smuQ&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8m0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=53b67686\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4D1Oeh0smuQ</a><br />\n<br />\n我地一路都好鐘意香港抗爭既歌，覺得好激勵好感人，但係發現好少英文version既歌，就諗住咁趁一週年，作翻一首做紀念。<br />\n<br />\n我地呢次係第一次作詞，第一次作曲，第一係剪片，第一次唱歌，所以有好多好多好多地方都做得唔好，希望大家屌得細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n15/6 係梁烈士逝世一週年，希望大家都唔好忘記佢既犧牲，記住佢既遺願，抗爭到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/pig.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"7b57abffb78516ced6ebde0e55eeab423b915186","tid":2064851,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T06:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06086475a10a13165cfa354d6dfffb197e345631","tid":2064851,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T06:44:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/mouse.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a767a1b69b91916e616f8cf53311e11d465dbe6c","tid":2064851,"uid":32063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T06:45:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/pig.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0cbf6fbd1403cf51e1670ee0ed5555518a207c2","tid":2064851,"uid":271807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T06:49:40.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"74b9c7cc36ac7650ce48b0340ca06fa2a360d5d2","tid":2064851,"uid":322240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b57abffb78516ced6ebde0e55eeab423b915186","tid":2064851,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T06:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:43:10.000Z","msg":"作嗰陣終於體會到作歌既人既辛苦<br />\n辛苦曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df705ddaf4afd00a6a8e86e3e89dbb09576ebde9","tid":2064851,"uid":288370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:53:00.000Z","msg":"支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n曲詞都作得好好 選圖亦都令人感動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a741a6f1cd251a70e25fea43e3936216cb606fd6","tid":2064851,"uid":322249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/pig.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/dog.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/mouse.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/cat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/flower.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34d98f814fe743baf7c7180cd0f8c22b0f261b9","tid":2064851,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:07:03.000Z","msg":"keep住作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac340edc3e3d748fa33cad22a4b64dec8785cec9","tid":2064851,"uid":322240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T11:21:54.000Z","msg":"Petals Rain 漫天紛花<br />\n<br />\nEarly summer gloom devours the land we share 初夏的陰暗籠罩住我們的家園<br />\nObliterates the once valued promises. 泯掉曾經的諾言<br />\nStarlight obscures reality&rsquo;s honest glare 真相之光被刺眼的星光遮蓋<br />\nDrains away the vigour of the orchids 繁星悄悄地吞噬洋紫荊僅餘的氣息<br />\n<br />\nAnd the flowers resound in the silent night,  在寂靜的夜晚迴盪著花朵的哀鳴<br />\n&Icirc;The hunger for freedom ignites, 對自由的飢渴在漆黑之中重燃<br />\nTogether, taking the valour to fight, 請賦予我們反抗的勇氣<br />\nLet our voices resonate as lucent light. 讓我們的吶喊能在城市中泛起希望的光澤<br />\n <br />\nOn the edge there casted a shadow, 在邊緣上屹立著一扇孤獨剪影<br />\nCollapsed at 88 Queensway Road. 倒塌在88號金鐘道之下<br />\nAshes to ashes, dust to dust, 塵歸塵，土歸土<br />\nLet gravity awaken souls. 唯願墮落的生命能換來靈魂的甦醒<br />\n<br />\nA long way down the petals flee, 花瓣緩緩飄落<br />\nFlicker with the wind to the field of free. 隨風搖曳至自由的遠方<br />\nPetals rain kisses the land, 漫天飛舞的花瓣如雨一樣落下<br />\nOne day in triumph we&rsquo;ll meet again. 於勝利之際，我們會相約在煲底相見<br />\n<br />\nOn the Lennon Walls carved the city&rsquo;s prayer; 在連儂牆上，刻著城市的悲歌<br />\nOn the Baltic Way a thousand hearts aligned. 在波羅的海之路上，千萬顆心為著同一夢想跳動<br />\nWinter&rsquo;s on fire, flow free like water. 如凜冬烈火一樣，誓為自由而戰；如流水一樣，靈活善變<br />\nIt&rsquo;s the revolution of our times. 我們為這時代的革命拼搏到底<br />\n<br />\nWhen the early dawn spills sprinkles of sunshine, 當黎明降臨，旭日升起<br />\nFlowers blossom far and wide. 眼前遍地開花<br />\nWe&rsquo;ll defend our city in the name of pride. 我們會以愛之名捍衛自己的土地<br />\nIn the courageous siege, spirits collide. 在腥風血雨的圍城之中，執戟相交，人們各為自己的理想拼搏到底<br />\n <br />\nPetals bleed in flare and smoke. 在煙霧星火之中，花瓣濺下殷紅涙<br />\nYou unblind the goddess, undress her robe. 你強迫正義女神撐開雙眼，橫蠻地搶走她的長袍<br />\nRiotous scarlet, riotous violet, 革命抹上花朵的血紅嫣紫<br />\nSwear to cling on in withering hope. 洋紫荊在凋零的曙光之中緊抓住那一絲希望<br />\n<br />\nA long way down the petals flee,  花瓣緩緩飄落<br />\nFlicker with the wind to the field of free. 隨風搖曳至自由的遠方<br />\nPetals rain kisses the land, 漫天飛舞的花瓣如雨一樣落下<br />\nOne day in triumph we&rsquo;ll meet again.  於勝利之際，我們會相約在煲底相見<br />\n<br />\nShades of scarlet fade from sight, 點點緋紅消散在塵土之中<br />\nVanish in the void like the melting snow. 如細雪消融般無聲無色<br />\nBloom is the flower gleaming white, 綻放的是雪白純潔的花朵<br />\nBright as an aura, blossom and grow. 如同光明的花苞一樣，燦然動人<br />\n<br />\nIn Promised Land, the petals blow. 在應許之地，花瓣飛揚<br />\nWe lived, felt dawn, saw the sunset glow. 我們存在過，曾經沐浴在晨曦之下，亦仰望過璀燦落日 <br />\nLoved and were loved, and now we lie. 我們愛過，也曾被愛過，現在我們躺臥在<br />\nBeneath the black flag in the night. 國殤之花之下<br />\n <br />\nFly the flag with the emblem we contend. 隨著夜幕的降臨<br />\nThe flower we love unfurls, 漆黑的旗幟掛在旗桿之上<br />\nAs the night descends. 隨風飄揚"},{"pid":"bdd13ac7c73e9ad3d332e06a21d8aa6d7b1a5a18","tid":2064851,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T17:38:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/dog.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好聽 有啲傷感又有啲治癒"},{"pid":"19de9fc51f016694937ed4a410ddcd86b11fa4ea","tid":2064851,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T17:39:54.000Z","msg":"個MV又整得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲詞又靚"},{"pid":"2f5208df83df4cc57639daae72c2c574837bcb19","tid":2064851,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T17:40:26.000Z","msg":"推到多啲人